item.title: New Zealand’s Most Selective Dating Agency Connects Singles Throughout New Zealand
item.description: After years of running a talent agency, Sasha Madarasz felt ready to get out of the fast-paced film industry and make more of a difference in the world. She just didn’t know how she would do that. The answer came from her boyfriend at the time, who suggested she start a dating agency. See more
